<p><a class="neo-figure" style="box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); cursor: pointer; margin: 40px 0px; font-family: -apple-system, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Arial, &#39;Neo Heiti&#39;, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; display: inline !important;"><img src="http://wechatapppro-1252524126.file.myqcloud.com/app80CX1DoD4392/image/ueditor/35952600_1550633553.png" style="box-sizing: inherit; border-style: none; vertical-align: middle; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;" class="loadingclass"/></a></p><p style="box-sizing: inherit; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; text-align: center; line-height: 1.5em;"><span style="box-sizing: inherit; font-weight: bolder;"></span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);">叶芝说：</span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);">假如除了人间，</span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);">没有天堂和地狱、炼狱和仙境的存在，</span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);">情感该如何表达？</span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);"><br/></span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);">有这样一个统计：</span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);">人类历史上销量达到5亿的系列书</span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);">上榜的只有一个</span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); font-weight: bold;">《哈利波特》</span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);"><br/></span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); font-weight: bold;">我们为何会对奇幻沉迷不已？</span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); font-weight: bold;">他将告诉你</span></p><p style="box-sizing: inherit; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; text-align: center;"><span style="box-sizing: inherit; font-weight: bolder;">▽</span></p><p style="box-sizing: inherit; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; text-align: center;"><span style="box-sizing: inherit; font-weight: bolder;">▼</span></p><p><a class="neo-figure" style="box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); cursor: pointer; margin: 40px 0px; display: block; font-family: -apple-system, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Arial, &#39;Neo Heiti&#39;, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; white-space: normal;"></a></p><p><a class="neo-figure" style="box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); cursor: pointer; margin: 40px 0px; display: block; font-family: -apple-system, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Arial, &#39;Neo Heiti&#39;, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; white-space: normal; text-align: center;"><img src="http://wechatapppro-1252524126.file.myqcloud.com/app80CX1DoD4392/image/ueditor/79021200_1550633553.jpg" title=".jpg" alt="奇幻文学-06.jpg" class="loadingclass"/></a></p><p style="box-sizing: inherit; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; text-align: center;"><span style="box-sizing: inherit; font-weight: bolder;">为你精选奇幻文学“四大名著”</span></p><p style="box-sizing: inherit; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px;"><br/></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);">《魔戒》</span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);">对宏大架空世界进行系统建构的元典</span></p><p style="text-align: cen