<p><a class="neo-figure" style="box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); cursor: pointer; margin: 40px 0px; font-family: -apple-system, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Arial, &#39;Neo Heiti&#39;, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; display: inline !important;"><img src="http://wechatapppro-1252524126.file.myqcloud.com/app80CX1DoD4392/image/ueditor/35952600_1550633553.png" style="box-sizing: inherit; border-style: none; vertical-align: middle; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;" class="loadingclass"/></a></p><p style="box-sizing: inherit; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; text-align: center; line-height: 1.5em;"><span style="box-sizing: inherit; font-weight: bolder;"></span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);">叶芝说：</span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);">假如除了人间，</span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);">没有天堂和地狱、炼狱和仙境的存在，</span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);">情感该如何表达？</span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);"><br/></span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);">有这样一个统计：</span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);">人类历史上销量达到5亿的系列书</span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);">上榜的只有一个</span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); font-weight: bold;">《哈利波特》</span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);"><br/></span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); font-weight: bold;">我们为何会对奇幻沉迷不已？</span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); font-weight: bold;">他将告诉你</span></p><p style="box-sizing: inherit; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; text-align: center;"><span style="box-sizing: inherit; font-weight: bolder;">▽</span></p><p style="box-sizing: inherit; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; text-align: center;"><span style="box-sizing: inherit; font-weight: bolder;">▼</span></p><p><a class="neo-figure" style="box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); cursor: pointer; margin: 40px 0px; display: block; font-family: -apple-system, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Arial, &#39;Neo Heiti&#39;, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; white-space: normal;"></a></p><p><a class="neo-figure" style="box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); cursor: pointer; margin: 40px 0px; display: block; font-family: -apple-system, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Arial, &#39;Neo Heiti&#39;, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; white-space: normal; text-align: center;"><img src="http://wechatapppro-1252524126.file.myqcloud.com/app80CX1DoD4392/image/ueditor/79021200_1550633553.jpg" title=".jpg" alt="奇幻文学-06.jpg" class="loadingclass"/></a></p><p style="box-sizing: inherit; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; text-align: center;"><span style="box-sizing: inherit; font-weight: bolder;">为你精选奇幻文学“四大名著”</span></p><p style="box-sizing: inherit; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px;"><br/></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);">《魔戒》</span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);">对宏大架空世界进行系统建构的元典</span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);">《纳尼亚传奇》</span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);">对西方宗教文化展开现代重述的范例</span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);">《冰与火之歌》</span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);">对史诗氛围进行精心营造的榜样</span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);">《哈利波特》</span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);">对现代社会展开另类观照的楷模</span></p><p style="box-sizing: inherit; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px;"><br/></p><p style="box-sizing: inherit; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; text-align: center;"><span style="box-sizing: inherit; font-weight: bolder;">串讲12个你不得不知的文学经典话题</span></p><p style="box-sizing: inherit; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px;"><span style="box-sizing: inherit; font-weight: bolder;"><br/></span></p><p style="box-sizing: inherit; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px;"><span style="box-sizing: inherit; font-weight: bolder;"><br/></span></p><h2 class="" style="white-space: normal; box-sizing: inherit; color: rgb(73, 73, 73); font-family: -apple-system, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Arial, &#39;Neo Heiti&#39;, sans-serif; text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: 17px; white-space: pre-wrap; caret-color: rgb(17, 17, 17); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"></span></h2><h2 class="" style="white-space: normal; box-sizing: inherit; color: rgb(73, 73, 73); font-family: -apple-system, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Arial, &#39;Neo Heiti&#39;, sans-serif; text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: 17px; white-space: pre-wrap; caret-color: rgb(17, 17, 17); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">&gt;&gt;进入经典&lt;&lt;</span></h2><p><a class="neo-figure" style="box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); cursor: pointer; margin: 40px 0px; display: block; font-family: -apple-system, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Arial, &#39;Neo Heiti&#39;, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; white-space: normal;"></a></p><p><a class="neo-figure" style="box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); cursor: pointer; margin: 40px 0px; display: block; font-family: -apple-system, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Arial, &#39;Neo Heiti&#39;, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; white-space: normal;"><img src="http://wechatapppro-1252524126.file.myqcloud.com/app80CX1DoD4392/image/ueditor/96375300_1550633553.jpg" title=".jpg" alt="奇幻文学大纲0219.jpg"/></a></p><h2 class="" style="white-space: normal; box-sizing: inherit; color: rgb(73, 73, 73); font-family: -apple-system, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Arial, &#39;Neo Heiti&#39;, sans-serif; text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: 17px; white-space: pre-wrap; caret-color: rgb(17, 17, 17); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"></span></h2><h2 class="" style="white-space: normal; box-sizing: inherit; color: rgb(73, 73, 73); font-family: -apple-system, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Arial, &#39;Neo Heiti&#39;, sans-serif; text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: 17px; white-space: pre-wrap; caret-color: rgb(17, 17, 17); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">&gt;&gt;你将获得&lt;&lt;</span></h2><p><span style="font-size: 17px; white-space: pre-wrap; caret-color: rgb(17, 17, 17); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><br/></span></p><p style="box-sizing: inherit; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; text-align: center; line-height: 1.5em;"><span style="box-sizing: inherit; font-weight: bolder;">&nbsp;“圈内人”必须知晓的硬核知识</span></p><p style="box-sizing: inherit; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; text-align: center; line-height: 1.5em;">奇幻成为流行的社会文化成因</p><p style="box-sizing: inherit; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; text-align: center; line-height: 1.5em;">四大奇幻经典别具一格的文学特色</p><p style="box-sizing: inherit; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; text-align: center; line-height: 1.5em;">魔法世界的搭建法则与世界观构思角度</p><p style="box-sizing: inherit; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; text-align: center; line-height: 1.5em;">天马行空的文字与现实竟是这样互动的！</p><p style="box-sizing: inherit; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px;"><br/></p><p style="box-sizing: inherit; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; text-align: center; line-height: 1.5em;"><span style="box-sizing: inherit; font-weight: bolder;">学者粉丝独家解析</span></p><p style="box-sizing: inherit; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; text-align: center; line-height: 1.5em;">学院派+粉丝视角</p><p style="box-sizing: inherit; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; text-align: center; line-height: 1.5em;">给你最地道的文化研究的视角与方法：</p><p style="box-sizing: inherit; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; text-align: center; line-height: 1.5em;">文学类型、现代批判、童话理论、时空层叠</p><p style="box-sizing: inherit; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; text-align: center; line-height: 1.5em;">宗教原理、母题流变、历史写照、政治隐喻<br/></p><p style="box-sizing: inherit; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; text-align: center; line-height: 1.5em;">将兴趣爱好变为学科专业原来是这种体验！&nbsp;</p><p style="box-sizing: inherit; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px;"><br/></p><p style="box-sizing: inherit; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; text-align: center; line-height: 1.5em;"><span style="box-sizing: inherit; font-weight: bolder;">文学与商业冲撞出的时代法则</span></p><p style="box-sizing: inherit; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; text-align: center; line-height: 1.5em;">“奇幻”“科幻”“玄幻”“魔幻”tag怎么打？</p><p style="box-sizing: inherit; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; text-align: center; line-height: 1.5em;">从文学变成文化产业，IP这么吃香？</p><p style="box-sizing: inherit; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; text-align: center; line-height: 1.5em;">周边生产、同人创作…</p><p style="box-sizing: inherit; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; text-align: center; line-height: 1.5em;">还有哪些你没涉足的领域？</p><p style="box-sizing: inherit; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; text-align: center; line-height: 1.5em;">这可不仅仅是属于粉丝的狂欢！</p><p style="box-sizing: inherit; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; line-height: 1.5em;"><br/></p><p style="box-sizing: inherit; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px;"><br/></p><h2 class="" style="white-space: normal; box-sizing: inherit; color: rgb(73, 73, 73); font-family: -apple-system, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Arial, &#39;Neo Heiti&#39;, sans-serif; text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: 17px; white-space: pre-wrap; caret-color: rgb(17, 17, 17); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"></span></h2><h2 class="" style="white-space: normal; box-sizing: inherit; color: rgb(73, 73, 73); font-family: -apple-system, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Arial, &#39;Neo Heiti&#39;, sans-serif; text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: 17px; white-space: pre-wrap; caret-color: rgb(17, 17, 17); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">&gt;&gt;你该来听&lt;&lt;</span></h2><p><span style="font-size: 17px; white-space: pre-wrap; caret-color: rgb(17, 17, 17); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><br/></span></p><p style="box-sizing: inherit; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; text-align: center; line-height: 1.5em;"><span style="box-sizing: inherit; font-weight: bolder;">奇幻爱</span>（死）<span style="box-sizing: inherit; font-weight: bolder;">好</span>（忠）<span style="box-sizing: inherit; font-weight: bolder;">者</span>（粉）</p><p style="box-sizing: inherit; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; text-align: center; line-height: 1.5em;">摩拳擦掌的<span style="box-sizing: inherit; font-weight: bolder;">奇幻文学写作者</span></p><p style="box-sizing: inherit; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; text-align: center; line-height: 1.5em;">处在最富想象力年纪的<span style="box-sizing: inherit; font-weight: bolder;">孩子们</span></p><p style="box-sizing: inherit; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; text-align: center; line-height: 1.5em;">希望培养孩子阅读兴趣的<span style="box-sizing: inherit; font-weight: bolder;">父母</span></p><p style="box-sizing: inherit; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; text-align: center; line-height: 1.5em;">准备将爱好发展为专业的<span style="box-sizing: inherit; font-weight: bolder;">学生朋友</span></p><p style="box-sizing: inherit; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; text-align: center; line-height: 1.5em;">以及——</p><p style="box-sizing: inherit; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; text-align: center; line-height: 1.5em;">对这个世界充满奇思妙想的所有人</p><p style="box-sizing: inherit; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px;"><br/></p><p style="box-sizing: inherit; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px;"><br/></p><h2 class="" style="white-space: normal; box-sizing: inherit; color: rgb(73, 73, 73); font-family: -apple-system, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Arial, &#39;Neo Heiti&#39;, sans-serif; text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: 17px; white-space: pre-wrap; caret-color: rgb(17, 17, 17); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"></span></h2><h2 class="" style="white-space: normal; box-sizing: inherit; color: rgb(73, 73, 73); font-family: -apple-system, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Arial, &#39;Neo Heiti&#39;, sans-serif; text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: 17px; white-space: pre-wrap; caret-color: rgb(17, 17, 17); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">&gt;&gt;来自学界的推荐&lt;&lt;</span></h2><p><a class="neo-figure" style="box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); cursor: pointer; margin: 40px 0px; display: block; outline-width: 0px; font-family: -apple-system, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Arial, &#39;Neo Heiti&#39;, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; white-space: normal;"></a></p><p><a class="neo-figure" style="box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); cursor: pointer; margin: 40px 0px; display: block; outline-width: 0px; font-family: -apple-system, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Arial, &#39;Neo Heiti&#39;, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; white-space: normal;"><img src="http://wechatapppro-1252524126.file.myqcloud.com/app80CX1DoD4392/image/ueditor/37945100_1550633554.jpg" style="box-sizing: inherit; border-style: none; vertical-align: middle; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;" class="loadingclass"/></a></p><p style="line-height:150%"><span style="font-size: 16px;"><strong><span style="font-family: 宋体;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">订</span>阅须知：</span></strong></span></p><p style="line-height:150%"><span style="font-family: 宋体; line-height: 150%; font-size: 16px;">1. 《去！把巫师叫醒——奇幻文学“四大名著”入门》&nbsp;为付费音频专栏，全部13期内容2月20日一次更新完毕；</span></p><p class="p1" style="white-space: normal;"><span class="s1">2.&nbsp;</span>已购买内容可在本公号均可收听或阅读；</p><p class="p1" style="white-space: normal;"><span class="s1">3. &nbsp;</span>请理解本专栏作为虚拟服务内容，购买成功后将不接受退款请求；</p><p class="p1" style="white-space: normal;"><span class="s1">4. &nbsp;</span>严禁任何形式的翻录或转载，严禁在第三方平台传播，违者将追究法律责任；<span class="s1">&nbsp;</span></p><p class="p1" style="white-space: normal;"><span class="s1">5.&nbsp;</span>订阅或付费过程中有任何问题，请公号后台留言，联系客服。</p><p style="line-height:150%"><span style="font-family: 宋体; line-height: 150%; font-size: 16px;"><br/></span></p><p style="line-height:150%"><span style="font-family: 宋体; line-height: 150%; font-size: 16px;"><br/></span></p><p style="line-height:150%"><span style="font-family: 宋体; line-height: 150%; font-size: 16px;"><br/></span></p><p style="line-height: 150%;"><span style="font-family: 宋体; line-height: 150%; font-size: 16px;"><br/></span></p>

第八讲 乔治·马丁的POV写作手法与《冰与火之歌》的多线叙事

